%h2 New Spot
!= error_messages_for 'spot'
- form_for new do |f|
  != label :spot, :url
  != f.text_field :url
  != label :spot, :tag_list, 'Tags'
  != f.text_field :tag_list
  != submit_tag('Submit')
%span
  Spot-a-tron will auto-tag your URL with 'artist', 'album', 'playlist', 'search' or 'track', depending on what you add.